     ceil(3)                MudOS (5 Sep 1994)                 ceil(3)
     NAME
          ceil() - round a float up to the nearest integer
     SYNOPSIS
          float ceil( float f );
     DESCRIPTION
          Returns (as a float) the nearest integer number equal to or
          greater than f.
     SEE ALSO
          floor(3), to_int(3), to_float(3)
     Page 1                                          (printed 3/16/95)
